column5: The Muskies Canada 2009 Muskie Odyssey is less than 2 weeks away! Don't miss this bi-annual Muskie Fest! Lots of great speakers, and tons of Muskie Tackle in one building!  http://www.muskiescanada.ca/whats_new/odyssey.php
this is a must see if your into toothy critters. see you there pigeontroller
will there be auction/silent auction prizes or trips this year?

I expect to be there. Always in the market for some new gear  Might pick up a net big enough to land a football player too. If anyone has a ginormous net they want to get rid of shoot me a pm and maybe I'll buy yours used at the show.

We have a huge raffle table and an incredible silent auction with custom lures, guided trips, fishing gear,etc.  All proceeds raised by Muskies Canada will directly impact the Muskie fishery in Ontario, an example of this would be the over 3000 7-10 inch fall fingerling stocked into Lake Simcoe in '07 an '08.
Excellent line-up Dax, this is gonna be another great show !!  See you on the 25th
Will be there on the Saturday
Would if I could.. but someone decided to get married that day !
